featured_reviews.review_id:
Raja Mia Masjid  is a Jumma Masjid at Gorabazar, Berhampore, Murshidabad.

All The people irrespective their caste, religion  can come and acquire knowledge of Islam.

All Muslims irrespective their sects can  perform their common prayers here.

Muslims can perform daily five time Swalat(Namaj) and pray Jumma Swalat here.

This place is also popular for activities regarding Dawa & Tabligue .

A Maqtab (Islamic education system) and a Library is also run by masjid committee successfully.
